# To show Trackme logs (actually it will show all device's log for the last several hours):
1. go to directory sdk\platform-tools, e.g.:
cd %USER%\AppData\Local\Android\Sdk\platform-tools
2. run adb.exe wiht param logcat and redirect output to some file (since there will be tons of lines)
adb logcat > c:/mylogcat.txt
3. in logs search for "TrackMe:"
